-- 'A Perfect Life' soars to top of U.S. bestsellers list
-- 
-- Thu Jul 31, 2014 01:08PM EDT
-- None



NEW YORK, July 31 (Reuters) - "A Perfect Life," the newest romance by prolific writer Danielle Steel, went straight to the top of the U.S. bestsellers list on Thursday.

